author: wn.com
title: Several mayors fail to be re-elected in WA local government elections
text: Several mayors fail to be re-elected in Western Australia's local government elections, while Canning council is set to return to business after its mayor and councillors were sacked last year for failing to provide good government to ratepayers. ...
